            <title><![CDATA[大众汽车考虑将斯柯达撤出中国市场]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>大众汽车正在考虑把</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>斯柯达（Skoda）</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>撤出中国，预计将于2023年做出决定。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>综合彭博社和路透社的报道，斯柯达首席执行官Klaus Zellmer在接受</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>德国汽车刊物《Automobilwoche》</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>采访时表示，“在中国的竞争非常激烈，我们将与中国合资方一起研究下一步应该怎么做。”</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>他说，预计将于2023年做出最终决定。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>他也提出，</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>斯柯达</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>可以考虑只在中国销售汽车，而不在中国生产汽车。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>大众汽车在给路透社的一份声明中表示，斯柯达不断检查其在国际市场的位置，并根据当时情况进行调整是正常的业务程序。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>报道称，中国冠病清零政策导致汽车行业供应链大范围中断，大众汽车已经把今年在中国市场的销售目标下调约14%。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

